{"tid":1578441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙嘴唱中国国歌  遊行愛国人士被市民包圍   警方護送上警車離開","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T06:44:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e293276a993284171aee8944f16f19a7ca1dbb","tid":1578441,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"早前有人發起周三尖沙嘴廣東道唱國歌及遊行活動，由於活動臨時改期，有愛國人士不滿，一度拒絕離開。警方到場維持秩序，又築成人鏈戒備。<br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴海港城附近，下午約1時30分，有約30至40支持香港警察的市民聚集，又高叫「支持香港警察」等口號。不過由於活動臨時改期，有愛國人士不滿，手持中國國旗揮動，又一度拒絕離開。<br />\n<br />\n期間有反修例示威者高呼「五大訴求，缺一不可」的口號，其後有多名愛國人士被市民包圍，雙方一度發生口角，最後愛國人士由警方護送上警車離開。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1594042/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E5%94%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%AD%B7%E9%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0d25f9e19dee1e924fd8c1d2cad171fd31a695a9","tid":1578441,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c315bb1b0ac44802c8a91b7b32b1f767eae445","tid":1578441,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=